My post was not meant to deter anyone from continuing to improve QS and 
its utility for all English speakers.  I have been advocating QS for 
decades now.  You cannot imagine how pleased I am to see these new 
proposals and work being done.  We have had what previously would have 
been a year&#39;s total of messages sent in the last few weeks.  Very exciting!

I have been writing QS so long, that I forgot, or, perhaps, didn&#39;t 
understand, that what seems second nature to me may not be so obvious to 
a newbie with no experience in phonemic writing.

Paige

